{"tid":1944034,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"支那人疑似冒充順豐電話詐騙案！！","createTime":"2020-03-26T06:38:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-26T07:21:48.000Z","uid":70786,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"f809edb13a3ee99979f70c2d4c9bee341a679984","tid":1944034,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T06:38:37.000Z","msg":"打嚟話係順豐，有件快件派咗幾次都唔成功要註銷（廣東話）<br />\n我心諗屌你老母我屋企日撚日有人呀死柒頭，仲有我根本就冇等緊收順豐快件<br />\n另外我從來冇將屋企電話交俾順豐，佢又會打嚟我屋企咁撚犀利喎<br />\n<br />\n然後轉駁咗去個支那接線生<br />\n聽到佢用支那話講你好，就即刻CUT撚佢線<br />\n<br />\n我屌你D支那人老母，冇工開咪叫個女做雞囉<br />\n男嘅咪走去打劫D雞囉，走嚟呃鳩香港人做乜撚柒野<br />\n仆街中武肺死撚晒咪唔怕失業囉<br />\n真係火撚滾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eed8fb1a59f9788262c559d36c940a024ef7250","tid":1944034,"uid":285371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T06:39:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65e2d2401a776d9a8f811fb66960b65ad4b1b096","tid":1944034,"uid":69746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T06:40:10.000Z","msg":"點解唔撚番佢"},{"pid":"6dfbe160c40a849a15d93e14dec45e8354de0e8b","tid":1944034,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T06:40:20.000Z","msg":"大家小心D<br />\n嚟緊會愈嚟愈多同類型事件發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能係支那人想呃鳩香港人回血"},{"pid":"5555d1b7472dae0c39a9bffc442bf98598dc90e7","tid":1944034,"uid":154533,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T06:40:34.000Z","msg":"其實呢d電話都已經好多年 有咩好講"},{"pid":"67c27f588676273d885bbc87f543916b6632e4d1","tid":1944034,"uid":201374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65e2d2401a776d9a8f811fb66960b65ad4b1b096","tid":1944034,"uid":69746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T06:40:10.000Z","msg":"點解唔撚番佢"},"citedBy":0